description: Try our easy to follow Chicken, Quinoa & Vegetable Salad recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Chicken salad,Seafood free,Wheat free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Chicken,Sesame free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Chicken, Quinoa & Vegetable Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place quinoa into a small saucepan with cold water. Place over high heat and bring to the boil. Simmer, covered, for 8-10 minutes or until quinoa is tender. Drain and rinse under cold water.
Add to lunch container with reserved salad. Shred reserved cooked chicken and add to salad. Take reserved dressing in a small container.
